          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill removes conditions on the designation of Puerto Rico as a qualified opportunity zone. In general, a <i>qualified opportunity zone</i> is an economically-distressed community where new investment may be eligible for preferential tax treatment.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-07-06T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
